{"tha-ap7:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap7:0.2":"Buddhavagga ","tha-ap7:0.3":"7 Punnamantaniputtattheraapadana ","tha-ap7:1.1":"“Ajjhayako mantadharo, ","tha-ap7:1.2":"tinnam vedana paragu; ","tha-ap7:1.3":"Purakkhatomhi sissehi, ","tha-ap7:1.4":"upagacchim naruttamam. ","tha-ap7:2.1":"Padumuttaro lokavidu, ","tha-ap7:2.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap7:2.3":"Mama kammam pakittesi, ","tha-ap7:2.4":"sankhittena mahamuni. ","tha-ap7:3.1":"Taham dhammam sunitvana, ","tha-ap7:3.2":"Abhivadetvana satthuno; ","tha-ap7:3.3":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap7:3.4":"Pakkamim dakkhinamukho. ","tha-ap7:4.1":"Sankhittena sunitvana, ","tha-ap7:4.2":"vittharena abhasayim; ","tha-ap7:4.3":"Sabbe sissa attamana, ","tha-ap7:4.4":"sutvana mama bhasato; ","tha-ap7:4.5":"Sakam ditthim vinodetva, ","tha-ap7:4.6":"buddhe cittam pasadayum. ","tha-ap7:5.1":"Sankhittenapi desemi, ","tha-ap7:5.2":"vittharena tathevaham; ","tha-ap7:5.3":"Abhidhammanayannuham, ","tha-ap7:5.4":"kathavatthuvisuddhiya; ","tha-ap7:5.5":"Sabbesam vinnapetvana, ","tha-ap7:5.6":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap7:6.1":"Ito pancasate kappe, ","tha-ap7:6.2":"caturo suppakasaka; ","tha-ap7:6.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap7:6.4":"catudipamhi issara. ","tha-ap7:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap7:7.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap7:7.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap7:7.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap7:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma punno mantaniputto thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap7:9.1":"Punnamantaniputtattherassapadanam pancamam. "}